---
import Page from '@layouts/Page.astro';
---

<Page
  title="申請入會"
  description="加入國際醫療減碳協會，與志同道合的醫療永續先驅共同推動台灣醫療淨零轉型。"
>
  <div class="container page-content">

    <header class="page-header">
      <h1 class="page-title">申請入會</h1>
      <p class="page-lead">
        成為協會會員，享有專業輔導資源，並加入推動台灣醫療淨零轉型的行列。
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="join-layout">

      <div class="join-benefits">
        <h2 class="section-heading">會員權益</h2>
        <ul class="benefits-list">
          <li class="benefit-item">
            <span class="benefit-item__icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="benefit-item__title">免費碳盤查輔導</h3>
              <p class="benefit-item__desc">全程享有協會專業團隊的 ISO 14064-1 碳盤查輔導，從啟動到第三方認證。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="benefit-item">
            <span class="benefit-item__icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="benefit-item__title">能源管理系統建置</h3>
              <p class="benefit-item__desc">協助規劃與建置符合 ISO 50001 精神的能源管理制度與監控系統。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="benefit-item">
            <span class="benefit-item__icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="benefit-item__title">ESG 報告撰寫</h3>
              <p class="benefit-item__desc">協助撰寫符合 GRI 框架的永續報告，強化院所對外揭露與品牌形象。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="benefit-item">
            <span class="benefit-item__icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="benefit-item__title">補助申請協助</h3>
              <p class="benefit-item__desc">媒合政府節能補助資源，協助院所申請能源局、環境部等相關補助計畫。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="benefit-item">
            <span class="benefit-item__icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="benefit-item__title">研討會與知識交流</h3>
              <p class="benefit-item__desc">優先受邀參加協會舉辦的專業研討會、工作坊與國際交流活動。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="join-form-section">
        <h2 class="section-heading">填寫申請表</h2>
        <form
          class="join-form"
          data-mailto-form
          data-mailto="info@crinhealthcare.org"
          data-subject="新會員申請 — 國際醫療減碳協會"
          novalidate
        >
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="name" class="form-label">
              聯絡人姓名
              <span class="form-required" aria-label="必填">*</span>
            </label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="name"
              name="name"
              data-label="聯絡人姓名"
              class="form-input"
              required
              autocomplete="name"
              placeholder="請輸入您的姓名"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="organization" class="form-label">
              機構名稱
              <span class="form-required" aria-label="必填">*</span>
            </label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="organization"
              name="organization"
              data-label="機構名稱"
              class="form-input"
              required
              placeholder="醫院或機構全名"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email" class="form-label">
              電子郵件
              <span class="form-required" aria-label="必填">*</span>
            </label>
            <input
              type="email"
              id="email"
              name="email"
              data-label="電子郵件"
              class="form-input"
              required
              autocomplete="email"
              placeholder="your@hospital.gov.tw"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="phone" class="form-label">聯絡電話</label>
            <input
              type="tel"
              id="phone"
              name="phone"
              data-label="聯絡電話"
              class="form-input"
              autocomplete="tel"
              placeholder="02-XXXX-XXXX 或 0912-XXX-XXX"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="message" class="form-label">申請說明 / 備註</label>
            <textarea
              id="message"
              name="message"
              data-label="申請說明 / 備註"
              class="form-textarea"
              rows="5"
              placeholder="請說明貴機構目前的減碳現況，或您希望協會協助的具體事項。"
            ></textarea>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="form-submit">
            送出申請
          </button>
        </form>
        <script>
          import '@/scripts/mailto-form';
        </script>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</Page>

<style>
  .page-content {
    padding-block: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .page-header {
    max-width: 72ch;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .page-lead {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-loose);
  }

  .join-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .section-heading {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .benefits-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .benefit-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .benefit-item__icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-paper);
    border-radius: 9999px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .benefit-item__title {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .benefit-item__desc {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-normal);
  }

  .join-form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    background-color: var(--color-paper);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .form-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .form-label {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .form-required {
    color: #dc2626;
    margin-left: 2px;
  }

  .form-input,
  .form-textarea {
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-family: inherit;
    color: var(--color-text);
    background-color: var(--color-paper);
    transition: border-color var(--transition-fast), box-shadow var(--transition-fast);
    min-height: 44px;
  }

  .form-input:focus,
  .form-textarea:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--color-primary-pale);
  }

  .form-textarea {
    resize: vertical;
    min-height: 120px;
  }

  .form-submit {
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-2xl);
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-paper);
    border: none;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: inherit;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color var(--transition-fast);
    min-height: 48px;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  .form-submit:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-primary-dark);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .join-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
